&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;You’ll play a pivotal role in accelerating revenue growth through Dubber’s EMEA channel partners, driving adoption, growing pipeline and achieving ambitious sales targets.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;You will be the ultimate player coach, leading by example and managing your own Dubber partners. You will be responsible for tracking their activity, ensuring they are building and following up on leads and pipeline to achieve goals.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;Increasing the percentage of sales resource engagement across the partner and further demonstrating the value of Dubber to the partners. Reporting to the VP Sales, EMEA, you will take a very hands-on approach to both relationship management and consistently drive customer outcomes within the territory.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
