&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;Drive revenue growth across EMEA by developing strong partner relationships and engagement that deliver measurable results.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;Own and exceed sales targets, generating new opportunities and expanding revenue.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
