&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;Coach and support Partner Engagement reps to improve conversion rates and sales performance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;x_elementToProof&quot;&gt;Manage and optimise the partner sales pipeline, ensuring strong forecasting and efficient deal flow.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
